1
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:45,720
[Love in Pavilion]

2
00:01:46,370 --> 00:01:50,830
[Episode 24]

3
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:58,840
Next,

4
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:03,840
I, Li Quzhuo, the genius second son

5
00:02:04,730 --> 00:02:06,150
of the Li family from Peach Garden, will

6
00:02:06,150 --> 00:02:08,810
report our investigation results to everyone.

7
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:12,810
Huaizhu, try some of these raisins.
They're delicious.

8
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:17,300
Puppy Li, that's enough from you.

9
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,329
Get to the point.

10
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:27,130
At the spy's hideout, the information of which
was provided by Hongye,

11
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:29,960
and with Qinlan's help, of course,

12
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,079
we caught a spy.

13
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,150
I placed three talismans on him,

14
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:38,280
and so we found his lair.

15
00:02:36,570 --> 00:02:38,360
[Dungeon] [Li Garden]

16
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:41,800
Li... Garden!

17
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:45,380
The leader is a honey badger demon,

18
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,240
known as "Flathead,"

19
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:49,090
nicknamed "The Unkillable."

20
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:57,430
[National Preceptor's Residence, Beast Kingdom]

21
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,460
Go find me some new demons.

22
00:03:00,100 --> 00:03:02,360
If the demons you offered still can't be selected

23
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:05,310
in the new round of demon selection at the Drunken Dream Tower,

24
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:07,570
you all have to participate personally.

25
00:03:07,570 --> 00:03:08,200
Yes.

26
00:03:25,430 --> 00:03:28,030
It was nothing but a disobedient little demon.

27
00:03:28,590 --> 00:03:30,120
There's no need to cover up.

28
00:03:30,410 --> 00:03:33,230
Your dealings have nothing to do with me.

29
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:37,910
What? Are you still angry?

30
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:41,220
I was wrong.

31
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:43,890
I kept that indenture back then

32
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:46,130
just as a memento.

33
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,090
Memento?

34
00:03:48,740 --> 00:03:49,910
That's not what you said

35
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:51,770
when you threatened me back then.

36
00:03:51,829 --> 00:03:54,150
You said the indenture was in the hands of
someone you trust.

37
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,280
If you died,

38
00:03:56,370 --> 00:03:58,510
he'd immediately reveal the secret.

39
00:03:59,310 --> 00:04:01,650
For the sake of that deceased
Young Master Zhang,

40
00:04:01,650 --> 00:04:03,140
you would do anything.

41
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,650
So I had to keep a trump card.

42
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,370
Then let's cut to the chase.

43
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:11,010
The matter of killing Wangquan Hongye

44
00:04:11,010 --> 00:04:12,170
ends here.

45
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:14,250
I won't be threatened anymore.

46
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:18,670
So you also don't care about the Zhang
family's fate anymore?

47
00:04:18,670 --> 00:04:22,280
If Wangquan Hongye finds out you're my son,

48
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,600
what do you think

49
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,640
he'll do to the Zhang family?

50
00:04:31,630 --> 00:04:35,600
Wangquan Hongye suddenly came to visit
the Beast Kingdom in secret.

51
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:39,210
Have you considered what the reason

52
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,240
behind this could be?

53
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:46,360
Could it be that he's here specifically
to investigate you?

54
00:04:46,950 --> 00:04:48,150
What did you tell him?

55
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:49,600
Nothing, really.

56
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:51,960
It's just my speculation.

57
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:53,630
However,

58
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,680
you know Wangquan Hongye.

59
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,260
He's very clever

60
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:01,350
and ruthless in his methods.

61
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,620
If you don't kill him today,

62
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:06,290
in the future, will he spare you?

63
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:08,120
Will he spare the Zhang family?

64
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:10,380
Ran.

65
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:13,160
I am the one who did you wrong.

66
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:17,310
But that Young Master Zhang
has shown you kindness.

67
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,630
Fine.

68
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:24,750
I will go kill Wangquan Hongye.

69
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,040
But from now on,

70
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:31,720
you be the National Preceptor
of the Beast Kingdom,

71
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,650
and I'll be Dark Sword Zhang Zheng.

72
00:05:35,770 --> 00:05:38,560
I've... Been waiting for you to say that.

73
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:41,190
The Beast Kingdom's spies have launched
a comprehensive manhunt

74
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:42,920
to search for Wangquan Hongye.

75
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:46,790
As soon as there's any news,
they'll inform you immediately.

76
00:05:48,780 --> 00:05:50,510
We've been talking for a while.

77
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,100
You must be hungry.

78
00:05:53,659 --> 00:05:57,159
Would you like to stay and have
one last meal with me?

79
00:05:58,390 --> 00:06:00,160
The last time I cooked for you

80
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:02,800
was over 20 years ago.

81
00:06:04,610 --> 00:06:07,340
If only that Young Master Zhang were still alive.

82
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,240
He was so kind.

83
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,930
He would surely persuade you to agree.

84
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:32,240
Once you eat the meal I made
with my own hands,

85
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:37,000
you'll be mine forever.

86
00:07:18,030 --> 00:07:19,740
[Honey Badger Demon]

87
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:25,390
Snake demon.

88
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:35,200
We don't want your life.

89
00:07:35,730 --> 00:07:36,520
Tell us,

90
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,020
where's the assassin?

91
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:41,040
You think you can leave?

92
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:49,530
What are you all waiting for?

93
00:07:49,530 --> 00:07:52,990
Think about what would happen to you
if the information leaks.

94
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:56,550
You...

95
00:08:01,130 --> 00:08:02,900
What's brewing in this cauldron

96
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:04,940
are all herbs for pain relief
and life preservation.

97
00:08:04,940 --> 00:08:06,800
And the dosage is extremely high.

98
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:08,920
You're already at the end of your rope.

99
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,950
I can't die yet.

100
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,990
If I die,

101
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:14,630
these fools will immediately make mistakes.

102
00:08:14,630 --> 00:08:16,270
They won't even know how they died.

103
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:18,330
The reason you're living in such pain

104
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:20,750
is to protect these spies, isn't it?

105
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:26,090
Tell me where the assassin is,

106
00:08:26,170 --> 00:08:28,350
and I'll pretend I was never here.

107
00:08:29,130 --> 00:08:30,930
You've seen what we're capable of.

108
00:08:30,930 --> 00:08:32,470
You have no other choice.

109
00:08:54,270 --> 00:08:55,120
Is it here?

110
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:31,940
So it's you.

111
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:44,710
Master Zhang.

112
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,910
You tried to assassinate me in the Beast Kingdom.

113
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:50,470
Were you trying to betray the
entire Yiqi Alliance?

114
00:09:50,470 --> 00:09:52,550
I don't understand what
you're talking about.

115
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:54,000
Since you don't understand,

116
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,960
show me the wound on your leg.

117
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:08,200
Do you think

118
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,510
you can escape?

119
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:14,840
Hongye!

120
00:10:17,770 --> 00:10:19,900
This matter has nothing to do with her.

121
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,150
I'll go with you.

122
00:10:41,100 --> 00:10:43,960
So what you've been concerned about all along

123
00:10:44,590 --> 00:10:46,650
is Master Zhang, right, Miss Qingmu?

124
00:10:47,470 --> 00:10:51,130
Dark Sword Zhang Zheng, in his quest to
be the world's greatest swordsman,

125
00:10:51,130 --> 00:10:53,320
has been opposing Wangquan Manor at every turn.

126
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,390
That day when he tried to assassinate me at Ruyi Pavilion,

127
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:57,390
did you know about it and not tell me?

128
00:10:57,390 --> 00:10:58,240
Yes.

129
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:01,040
What else are you hiding from me?

130
00:11:16,430 --> 00:11:17,430
Hongye.

131
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:22,960
If I tell you Zhang Zheng had his reasons
for trying to assassinate you,

132
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,200
can you spare him?

133
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:27,240
You already believe in your heart
that I wouldn't spare him.

134
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:29,030
That's why you rushed here tonight,

135
00:11:29,030 --> 00:11:30,320
wanting to rescue him.

136
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,460
Hongye, you said it yourself that

137
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,890
he opposes Wangquan at every turn.

138
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:39,320
He's the biggest rival to your
Yiqi Alliance.

139
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,200
So?

140
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,910
So you think now that I know his secret,

141
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:43,960
I won't spare him,

142
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,930
and I won't spare the entire Zhang family.

143
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:47,910
Yuan, you...

144
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,320
So, is this

145
00:11:54,610 --> 00:11:56,410
the kind of person you think I am?

146
00:11:59,200 --> 00:11:59,910
Hongye.

147
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,600
I truly like him.

148
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:16,120
I'll tell you everything I know

149
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,000
right now.

150
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,640
That's how things stand.

151
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:25,270
I want to save him.

152
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,280
I want to kill Anayan.

153
00:12:27,870 --> 00:12:30,600
Zhang Zheng must have some leverage in her hands.

154
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,000
But Anayan wouldn't be so stupid

155
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:34,890
as to carry the evidence with her.

156
00:12:34,910 --> 00:12:37,710
She should've entrusted
the evidence to someone.

157
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:38,910
Once she's dead,

158
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:41,720
the evidence will be made public immediately.

159
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:45,920
You've already issued a standing kill order?

160
00:12:46,330 --> 00:12:47,860
The bounty is 10,000 taels.

161
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:49,890
I'll immediately give an order to recall it.

162
00:12:49,890 --> 00:12:51,420
I'll also inform Yitan right away.

163
00:12:51,420 --> 00:12:52,690
Activate your intelligence network

164
00:12:52,690 --> 00:12:54,750
and track all of Anayan's movements.

165
00:12:54,830 --> 00:12:56,490
If this person really exists,

166
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:59,180
he's probably hiding in the Yiqi Alliance.

167
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,960
Quickly, find someone to look into this.

168
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,960
Yuan will give you the information.

169
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:30,380
Finally, there's something to do.

170
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:31,150
Say it.

171
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,320
What great demon are we dealing with

172
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:35,000
that you need my help?

173
00:13:35,150 --> 00:13:36,630
He asked us to find someone

174
00:13:37,570 --> 00:13:39,430
hidden within the Yiqi Alliance.

175
00:13:39,910 --> 00:13:42,310
This person has leverage over Zhang Zheng.

176
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:44,120
Dark Sword Zhang Zheng?

177
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:47,580
Since when did Hongye get involved with him?

178
00:13:55,760 --> 00:13:58,090
[Three days later]

179
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,500
You must be hungry.

180
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,250
Go ahead and eat.

181
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:15,790
What?

182
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:18,050
Have you decided how to kill me?

183
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:19,750
Is this my last meal?

184
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,650
There's no asparagus in it.

185
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:23,840
Try it.

186
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,200
Wangquan Hongye,

187
00:14:30,630 --> 00:14:32,090
what exactly are you up to?

188
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:37,040
In your eyes,

189
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:41,840
am I really such a despicable person?

190
00:14:44,090 --> 00:14:47,380
Dongfang Huaizhu is that sword attendant
from the Nangong family.

191
00:14:47,380 --> 00:14:50,610
The Nangong family incident was your joint doing.

192
00:14:52,420 --> 00:14:53,680
So you still remember.

193
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:57,600
It seems besides worrying about Qingmu Yuan,

194
00:14:57,600 --> 00:15:02,660
you're also worried that the Zhang family will become
the next Nangong family, aren't you?

195
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,360
Let me ask you a question.

196
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,000
Go ahead.

197
00:15:07,550 --> 00:15:09,720
Nangong Ye has tried to woo you many times.

198
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:11,670
You've had many chances to surpass me and

199
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:14,000
become the world's greatest swordsman
using the demon core.

200
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,120
Why did you refuse?

201
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:16,910
I want to defeat you,

202
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:20,240
but with the Dark Sword.

203
00:15:22,790 --> 00:15:24,450
It must be with the Dark Sword.

204
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:30,400
Is it because of the exhortation

205
00:15:30,430 --> 00:15:32,030
that person entrusted to you

206
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:34,040
with her life?

207
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:40,510
Yuan has told me

208
00:15:41,090 --> 00:15:42,340
your secret.

209
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:49,850
Here's something I've just obtained.

210
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:47,570
[Indenture]

211
00:15:50,370 --> 00:15:52,870
[Indenture]

212
00:15:52,870 --> 00:15:54,320
[Signed by: Anayan]
[Signed by: Zhang Jian]

213
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,680
Anayan is very cunning.

214
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:04,530
When selling her son that day,

215
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:07,930
she made Master Zhang personally
handwrite this indenture.

216
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:10,900
Although Master Zhang used a false name,

217
00:16:11,090 --> 00:16:13,420
once you compare the handwriting,

218
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:15,900
you'll know whose handwriting it is.

219
00:16:17,460 --> 00:16:18,640
Wangquan Hongye.

220
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:21,380
What exactly do you want to do?

221
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:26,970
So this is what has been threatening you
for so long?

222
00:16:29,670 --> 00:16:30,610
No matter what,

223
00:16:33,340 --> 00:16:35,400
I won't be threatened by you anymore.

224
00:16:54,460 --> 00:16:56,910
I really don't quite understand you anymore.

225
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,370
If I say

226
00:16:58,510 --> 00:16:59,270
I've always been grateful

227
00:16:59,270 --> 00:17:01,200
to have someone like you by my side,

228
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:03,610
a swordsman who could surpass me at any time,

229
00:17:03,610 --> 00:17:04,810
would you believe me?

230
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:10,880
It seems you don't.

231
00:17:12,420 --> 00:17:15,339
Then can I exchange this gift for

232
00:17:16,349 --> 00:17:18,510
a chance for you to know me next time?

233
00:17:24,970 --> 00:17:26,589
The wontons are getting cold.

234
00:17:26,589 --> 00:17:27,420
Eat up.

235
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:59,250
In the Yiqi Alliance, the Wangquan Sword
commands respect from the masses,

236
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:01,720
while the Dark Sword protects the realm
and strengthens itself.

237
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:04,890
These two have never been in conflict.

238
00:18:14,110 --> 00:18:15,710
Are you really letting me go?

239
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:17,750
I know your prejudice runs deep,

240
00:18:17,770 --> 00:18:19,300
and it won't change easily.

241
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:21,350
But I still hope

242
00:18:22,030 --> 00:18:23,960
you can understand my intentions.

243
00:18:30,990 --> 00:18:32,440
If I'm not mistaken,

244
00:18:32,790 --> 00:18:36,050
this jade piece was given to you
by Young Master, wasn't it?

245
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:40,110
Young Master was such a good person.

246
00:18:40,510 --> 00:18:42,400
What he left you before he passed away

247
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:43,640
must not be a shackle.

248
00:18:46,360 --> 00:18:47,950
Don't feel guilty.

249
00:18:48,300 --> 00:18:50,480
This is all my own choice.

250
00:18:52,110 --> 00:18:53,750
It has nothing to do with you.

251
00:18:54,840 --> 00:18:58,140
I hope you can live well.

252
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:02,860
Take good care of yourself.

253
00:19:06,530 --> 00:19:07,860
As long as you live well.

254
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:11,960
That's the only thing I want from you.

255
00:19:24,310 --> 00:19:25,450
Wangquan Hongye.

256
00:19:25,850 --> 00:19:28,710
It was Anayan who instructed me
to assassinate you.

257
00:19:29,570 --> 00:19:32,230
I think she's been acting on the ruler's orders.

258
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,620
She's the owner of the Drunken Dream Tower.

259
00:19:35,620 --> 00:19:36,800
Recently, she's been selecting demons

260
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:38,350
to do something very dangerous.

261
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:40,610
I already have some clues on this matter.

262
00:19:40,740 --> 00:19:41,500
Zhang Zheng,

263
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:44,330
can I ask you for a favor?

264
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:45,440
What is it?

265
00:19:49,770 --> 00:19:52,000
Zhang Zheng... Is pretty good.

266
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,640
Better than me?

267
00:19:58,440 --> 00:20:00,440
He and Qingmu Yuan make a good match.

268
00:20:04,110 --> 00:20:06,040
Then why didn't Yuan come herself?

269
00:20:06,870 --> 00:20:10,070
There are some things they have to figure out
on their own.

270
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:21,790
My Lady,

271
00:21:21,810 --> 00:21:23,670
what are you looking at?

272
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:25,270
Nothing.

273
00:21:33,130 --> 00:21:34,300
Meng Yun, I'm going out for a while.

274
00:21:34,300 --> 00:21:35,390
Going out again?

275
00:21:35,510 --> 00:21:37,530
By the way, where's the sword tassel
I ordered earlier?

276
00:21:37,530 --> 00:21:38,670
You mean this?

277
00:22:15,520 --> 00:22:16,440
That night,

278
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,200
you already knew.

279
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:26,720
Sorry.

280
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:32,400
I used a smoke bomb on you that day.

281
00:22:33,420 --> 00:22:34,400
So, now you know

282
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:39,940
I'm Young Master's stand-in, right?

283
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,900
Yes, and there's more.

284
00:22:43,340 --> 00:22:44,070
What?

285
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:47,830
Now I know why after we turned 18,

286
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:49,770
you stopped talking to me.

287
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:52,460
The shackles on your heart

288
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:53,830
are too heavy.

289
00:22:54,240 --> 00:22:56,100
[Those who love you hope you live for yourself.]

290
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:02,280
Zhang Zheng!

291
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:04,720
Zhang Zheng, what's wrong with you?

292
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:05,680
Zhang Zheng!

293
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:11,200
There are blue scales under your eyes.

294
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:13,800
It's the demon poison of
the Nine-headed Bird.

295
00:23:14,390 --> 00:23:16,120
Your eye color has changed too.

296
00:23:16,190 --> 00:23:18,200
The demon poison has entered
your bloodstream.

297
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:19,490
How could this happen?

298
00:23:21,270 --> 00:23:24,000
Anayan. It must be Anayan.

299
00:23:25,820 --> 00:23:26,550
Zhang Zheng!

300
00:23:28,790 --> 00:23:30,830
The bird poison has reached your heart.

301
00:23:30,830 --> 00:23:32,380
Even if I take you back to Ruyi Pavilion,

302
00:23:32,380 --> 00:23:33,940
it'll be too late to detoxify you.

303
00:23:33,940 --> 00:23:35,230
Zhang Zheng.

304
00:23:38,310 --> 00:23:41,750
This is the only way now.

305
00:23:42,240 --> 00:23:45,170
The blood exchange cauldron of the Leech Demon Clan.

306
00:23:45,630 --> 00:23:47,560
I can only exchange blood with him,

307
00:23:47,590 --> 00:23:49,520
draw the demon poison into my body,

308
00:23:50,030 --> 00:23:53,370
and try to suppress it before the poison
reaches his heart.

309
00:24:00,370 --> 00:24:01,330
Zhang Zheng.

310
00:24:02,070 --> 00:24:04,200
I want you to be indebted to me forever.

311
00:25:12,760 --> 00:25:15,010
[Those who love you hope you live for yourself.]

312
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:18,550
What just happened?

313
00:26:25,590 --> 00:26:26,350
Be careful.

314
00:26:31,070 --> 00:26:31,830
What?

315
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:36,030
Are you more interested in this thing
than in me?

316
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:38,880
Why are you jealous?

317
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:41,850
You know you're always in my heart.

318
00:26:42,220 --> 00:26:44,760
Forget it. I've seen through you long ago.

319
00:26:45,510 --> 00:26:47,270
You only dare to call me over

320
00:26:47,270 --> 00:26:48,930
when Miss Huaizhu isn't home.

321
00:26:49,070 --> 00:26:54,400
Aren't you just worried that someone will find out and stop you
from marrying into their family?

322
00:26:56,510 --> 00:26:57,910
You're overthinking it.

323
00:26:58,270 --> 00:27:01,600
I, Jin Renfeng, have plenty of ways
to make a name for myself.

324
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:03,480
What ways?

325
00:27:04,110 --> 00:27:05,170
Tell me about them.

326
00:27:08,980 --> 00:27:11,730
Could it be... This?

327
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,770
I'll tell you next time.

328
00:27:15,950 --> 00:27:17,350
It's getting late today.

329
00:27:20,590 --> 00:27:22,230
Alright. Whatever you say.

330
00:27:22,680 --> 00:27:24,480
After all, you're the one I like.

331
00:27:26,350 --> 00:27:27,810
Take your time to study it.

332
00:27:40,020 --> 00:27:42,480
This is indeed a superior magical artifact.

333
00:27:43,030 --> 00:27:44,800
It was fixed so quickly.

334
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:47,270
Jin Renfeng.

335
00:27:52,420 --> 00:27:53,900
Lord Jiuhuo, is that you?

336
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:57,510
That Anayan is incompetent.

337
00:27:58,400 --> 00:28:00,160
Go check on the Beast Kingdom.

338
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:03,030
Yes.

339
00:28:23,350 --> 00:28:25,280
What do you want to talk to me about?

340
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:26,030
Go ahead.

341
00:28:28,090 --> 00:28:31,100
Qinlan, you love Huaizhu very much,
don't you?

342
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:32,590
Of course.

343
00:28:32,590 --> 00:28:34,920
Then if there's someone
Huaizhu really likes,

344
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,310
but you don't like them,

345
00:28:36,380 --> 00:28:37,460
what would you do?

346
00:28:40,810 --> 00:28:43,140
Well, answer a few questions for me first.

347
00:28:45,110 --> 00:28:47,270
Do you know what Huaizhu likes to eat?

348
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:48,880
Yin Cake and fish.

349
00:28:48,920 --> 00:28:49,960
Then what is she good at?

350
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:51,180
She's not skilled in the four arts.

351
00:28:51,180 --> 00:28:52,540
She doesn't like composing poems,

352
00:28:52,540 --> 00:28:54,680
nor can she cook, do laundry, or make beds.

353
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:57,390
But she likes fighting and magic duels.

354
00:28:57,510 --> 00:28:58,720
Very good.

355
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:01,590
So do you know why she doesn't fight easily?

356
00:29:03,890 --> 00:29:06,310
Because Divine Fire Villa has
restrained her.

357
00:29:06,310 --> 00:29:07,880
Although she's content with it,

358
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:09,200
I feel sorry for her.

359
00:29:09,790 --> 00:29:11,390
If you two get together,

360
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:13,200
your Wangquan Sword

361
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:15,500
and her Dongfang Spiritual Blood

362
00:29:15,790 --> 00:29:17,520
will be burdens

363
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:18,830
for both of you.

364
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:22,820
The reason why I like the Mask Group Leader

365
00:29:23,030 --> 00:29:24,680
is that Huaizhu likes him.

366
00:29:25,070 --> 00:29:26,350
What she fell in love with at first sight

367
00:29:26,350 --> 00:29:27,880
is actually what she yearns
for in her heart,

368
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:29,110
the sense of freedom.

369
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:31,290
Do you understand now?

370
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:33,200
I do.

371
00:29:33,750 --> 00:29:36,240
Qinlan, you really love Huaizhu.

372
00:29:37,510 --> 00:29:39,160
Now you can back off, right?

373
00:29:41,080 --> 00:29:42,160
Now,

374
00:29:42,360 --> 00:29:44,560
I'm even more determined to pursue her.

375
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:47,680
Why are you so stubborn?

376
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:55,530
Because I also love Huaizhu very much.

377
00:29:55,710 --> 00:29:59,400
I believe I can give her
what she yearns for.

378
00:30:18,090 --> 00:30:19,240
What is this?

379
00:30:20,070 --> 00:30:22,590
This is called the Noble Lady
Leg-breaking Talisman.

380
00:30:22,590 --> 00:30:26,350
It's a masterpiece I poured my heart
and soul into creating.

381
00:30:26,700 --> 00:30:29,430
It's even more powerful than
my brother's works.

382
00:30:29,490 --> 00:30:31,250
So, do you want one?

383
00:30:36,690 --> 00:30:38,280
You look so dejected.

384
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,290
It's not like you at all.

385
00:30:42,090 --> 00:30:43,020
Puppy Li.

386
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:45,880
You have an older brother, right?

387
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:46,720
Yes, I do.

388
00:30:48,030 --> 00:30:50,720
Then do you know what your brother likes

389
00:30:50,720 --> 00:30:51,920
and what he doesn't like?

390
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:52,720
No, I don't.

391
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:53,780
He's never told me.

392
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:56,790
Being so carefree,

393
00:30:56,790 --> 00:30:59,790
aren't you worried you may
hurt your brother's feelings?

394
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:00,720
I'm so excellent.

395
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:02,520
Why should my brother feel hurt?

396
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:07,400
I... Really like myself.

397
00:31:08,350 --> 00:31:09,960
I have a great personality,

398
00:31:10,240 --> 00:31:11,750
and I look pretty good.

399
00:31:12,440 --> 00:31:14,030
A lot of people love me,

400
00:31:14,510 --> 00:31:16,040
and there are people I love.

401
00:31:16,310 --> 00:31:17,640
I can eat and sleep well.

402
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:19,740
Besides, I even eat more than others.

403
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:22,360
I'm really special, aren't I?

404
00:31:26,980 --> 00:31:28,310
What exactly happened?

405
00:31:30,940 --> 00:31:32,350
I just...

406
00:31:34,110 --> 00:31:35,510
Feel sorry for Huaizhu.

407
00:31:36,750 --> 00:31:38,350
She's so nice to me,

408
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:41,400
but I don't know how to repay her.

409
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:45,240
Well,

410
00:31:46,550 --> 00:31:48,350
you're thinking about it wrong.

411
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:51,350
Our older brothers and sisters raised us
to be carefree,

412
00:31:51,350 --> 00:31:52,680
naive, and daffy.

413
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:54,960
They're actually very happy about it.

414
00:31:55,110 --> 00:31:58,440
As for us, we should just keep
the gratitude in our hearts,

415
00:31:58,440 --> 00:32:00,110
and continue to let them see us live happily.

416
00:32:00,110 --> 00:32:01,440
That's all we need to do.

417
00:32:08,480 --> 00:32:10,660
I didn't expect you

418
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:14,890
to say such sensible things sometimes.

419
00:32:15,820 --> 00:32:17,510
Don't really treat me like a dog.

420
00:32:17,510 --> 00:32:19,040
Call me Quzhuo.

421
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:21,160
You are just Puppy Li.

422
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:22,510
No, call me Quzhuo.

423
00:32:22,510 --> 00:32:23,400
What Puppy Li?

424
00:32:24,070 --> 00:32:24,720
Hurry up.

425
00:32:33,830 --> 00:32:36,370
Go on, Puppy Li.

426
00:32:38,110 --> 00:32:40,170
Still refusing to admit you're a dog.

427
00:32:55,620 --> 00:32:57,440
Dongfang Huaizhu.

428
00:32:58,720 --> 00:33:00,680
You think you can escape?

429
00:33:04,060 --> 00:33:06,800
I've already become one with you.

430
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:11,320
I'm just temporarily suppressed for now.

431
00:33:20,830 --> 00:33:21,760
You fell asleep?

432
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,400
Lotus seed soup.

433
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:31,720
Go get ready after you finish it.

434
00:33:32,750 --> 00:33:35,150
Today is the annual Wulan Festival in the Beast Kingdom.

435
00:33:35,150 --> 00:33:36,420
I want to take you out

436
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:37,780
and give you a gift.

437
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:49,960
Rabbit. Rabbit.

438
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:54,880
Rabbit. Rabbit.

439
00:33:55,030 --> 00:33:55,810
I want this one.

440
00:33:55,810 --> 00:33:56,350
Okay.

441
00:33:56,350 --> 00:33:56,810
Rabbit.

442
00:33:58,000 --> 00:33:59,060
No need for change.

443
00:33:59,070 --> 00:33:59,830
Thank you.

444
00:34:01,790 --> 00:34:03,160
Is this for Qinlan?

445
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:04,570
It's for you.

446
00:34:04,750 --> 00:34:06,110
It's very sweet. Try it.

447
00:34:07,550 --> 00:34:10,320
Miss, I want that rabbit too.

448
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:16,110
You can have it.

449
00:34:16,670 --> 00:34:17,800
Thank you, Miss.

450
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,280
Let's go.

451
00:34:20,750 --> 00:34:22,110
We have a rabbit now.

452
00:34:28,190 --> 00:34:29,250
What are you doing?

453
00:34:29,280 --> 00:34:30,550
Huaizhu is out with Hongye.

454
00:34:30,550 --> 00:34:31,760
Why should you be worried?

455
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:35,159
It's exactly because it's Hongye that
I'm even more worried.

456
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:41,590
What's going on in that
little head of yours?

457
00:34:42,330 --> 00:34:44,659
I'm worried Huaizhu might be deceived.

458
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:49,110
Well, since you're so worried about her,

459
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:52,100
I'll let you see for yourself.

460
00:34:52,500 --> 00:34:53,630
So you'll know

461
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:54,860
that Hongye

462
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:57,710
is the best man Huaizhu could
entrust herself to.

463
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:59,710
Don't be so definitive.

464
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:01,320
What if after seeing it with my own eyes,

465
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:02,850
I dislike Hongye even more?

466
00:35:03,630 --> 00:35:04,830
Seeing is believing.

467
00:35:05,150 --> 00:35:05,710
Let's go.

468
00:35:23,030 --> 00:35:24,880
Here's your tea, sir.

469
00:35:25,550 --> 00:35:26,630
That outfit just now

470
00:35:26,630 --> 00:35:28,060
suits her perfectly.

471
00:35:28,150 --> 00:35:30,970
But the price is not cheap.

472
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:37,760
Thank you, sir.

473
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:38,920
Thank you, sir.

474
00:36:46,710 --> 00:36:47,900
If I were you,

475
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:50,040
I would respect her decision

476
00:36:50,150 --> 00:36:51,960
and let her choose who she likes.

477
00:37:00,190 --> 00:37:00,920
Wait for me.

478
00:37:21,860 --> 00:37:23,590
This is the gift I'm giving you.

479
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:27,400
A bowl of sweet porridge?

480
00:37:28,930 --> 00:37:30,530
The life of ordinary people.

481
00:37:30,570 --> 00:37:31,860
An ordinary day

482
00:37:32,010 --> 00:37:33,340
for an ordinary couple.

483
00:37:39,720 --> 00:37:40,550
Huaizhu.

484
00:37:41,570 --> 00:37:43,730
I know you prefer a quiet and simple life.

485
00:37:43,730 --> 00:37:44,930
What you yearn for

486
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:47,850
is just an ordinary, carefree life like this.

487
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:51,590
I believe we will live such a life.

488
00:37:52,510 --> 00:37:54,960
One day, I'm sure we will.

489
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:11,070
Do you still want to keep following them?

490
00:38:11,070 --> 00:38:11,800
Shut up.

491
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:25,600
Where are they going?

492
00:38:25,900 --> 00:38:27,300
It's the Wulan Festival.

493
00:38:28,030 --> 00:38:30,710
They're going to make wishes under
the Wulan Tree by Crescent Lake.

494
00:38:30,710 --> 00:38:33,440
Legend has it that if Crescent Lake
becomes Full Moon Lake,

495
00:38:33,440 --> 00:38:35,170
the wishes made will come true.

496
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:38,250
Do you want to go?

497
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:42,380
It's late.

498
00:38:42,590 --> 00:38:43,920
Won't you feel cold?

499
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:45,710
I won't.

500
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:47,670
I have the Dongfang Spiritual Blood.
